NORTH WOODMERE, L. I., Feb. 29—Mr. and Mrs. Max Gerson have made known the engagement of their daughter, Miss Beverly Faye Gerson, to Samuel Carl Himelstein. He is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Louis Himelstein of West Hartford, Conn.

A wedding in August is planned.

Miss Gerson, an alumna of Adelphi University, is attending the School of Library Science at the Pratt Institute and is with the Brooklyn Public Library.

Her fiancé, who graduated from Trinity College, is a student at the State University Downstate Medical Center.